"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-showbiz-lady-gaga-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-edith-piaf-river-seine-b1173189.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Showbiz  Sign up to our free weekly newsletter for exclusive competitions, offers and theatre ticket deals    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"AmericansingerLady Gagasang inFrenchduring her performance at the Paris Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old hid behind a plume of pink feathers as she walked down a set of golden stairs next to theRiver Seine, close toNotre Damecathedral.\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 657, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999800966182, \"rank\": 1.2989392115992568e-08, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The singer, real name Stefani Germanotta, appeared from behind the feathers and sang \\\"good evening, welcome to Paris\\\" before she engaged in a high-octane performance.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stefani Germanotta\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.786617983064404e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paparazzi singer, who performed alongside a group of dancers holding round pink, frilly props, wore a black bodice with a detachable black and pink ruffled skirt.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paparazzi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.808317205634726e-28, \"text\": \"Paparazzi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paparazzi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paparazzi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The musician is also reportedly set to perform a version ofEdith Piaf's La Vie en Rose alongsideCeline Dionas part of a glittering conclusion to the first ever opening ceremony being staged outside a stadium.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So far the event has seen a total of 85 boats carry the team delegations on a six-kilometre journey through the centre of Paris, with more than 300,000 spectators lining the banks of the river.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.786617983064404e-1